{
  "stem": "24814.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we got them to the rear as fast as we could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- well, we had to improvise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The old Army Medical Corps between wars was archaic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the-- the refuge of the incompetent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had stuff that hadn't been used since the Spanish-American War in 1900.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we got good, modern stuff when we went overseas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sulfa-- we had sulfa drugs-- didn't have penicillin yet-- and bandages and splints.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we improvised a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- yes, we could use pentothal by vein, or chloroform, the old-fashioned anesthetic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two or three quick whiffs of chloroform, you can set a bone quickly and let them come out of it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was scared all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- you had to do what you had to do, as they say nowadays, so I did it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it-- it's a terrifying experience, let me tell you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's worse and sicker-- as I described in my book, the first man I saw killed, when I suddenly realized what this is all about, was back in the line in December.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I looked out the window of my aid station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A shell went off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a big explosion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Someone screamed, medics, medics.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I grabbed my helmet and my aid kit and ran out across the field.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I yelled, where's the casualty?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the hands came up out of foxholes and pointed, over there, Doc.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they all got back in their foxholes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I suddenly realized, when you're a medic, you go out and get the wounded.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And an aid man and I got to this boy and his face was all blood.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was dabbing at it, looking for the wound.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The aid man kept trying to babble at me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't understand what he said.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
